="font: 12px/18px 돋움, Dotum, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;">아래와 같이 적용하오니, 내용 확인해 주시기 바랍니다.</div><div style="font: 12px/18px 돋움, Dotum, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"></div><div style="font: 12px/18px 돋움, Dotum, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;- 아 래 -</div><div style="font: 12px/18px 돋움, Dotum, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"></div><div style="font: 12px/18px 돋움, Dotum, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;"><span style="line-height: 1.5; font-family: 맑은고딕"; font-size:="" 10pt;"="">■&nbsp;</span><b>적용일자</b><span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>:<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><b><span style="color: rgb(255, 0, 0);">2015년 10월 12일</span></b>&nbsp;</div><div style="font: 12px/18px 돋움, Dotum, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"></div><div style="font: 12px/18px 돋움, Dotum, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;"><span style="line-height: 1.5; font-family: 맑은고딕"; font-size:="" 10pt;"="">■&nbsp;</span><b>적용 내용</b><span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span></div><div style="font: 12px/18px 돋움, Dotum, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;"><span style="color: rgb(255, 0, 0);"><b>&nbsp;</b></span></div><div style="font: 12px/18px 돋움, Dotum, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;"><span style="color: rgb(255, 0, 0);"><b><span style="font-size: 10pt;">&nbsp;◈ 사전에 인증, 등록된 번호만 문자전송 가능</span></b></span>&nbsp;</div><div style="font: 12px/18px 돋움, Dotum, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;">&nbsp; &nbsp;-. 미래부가 지정한 세칙에 맞는 번호만 전송가능</div><div style="font: 12px/18px 돋움, Dotum, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 인증 가능한 번호는 8자리~11자리 이내의 숫자만 허용</div><div style="font: 12px/18px 돋움, Dotum, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 030/050 번호는 12자리까지 등록가능</div><div style="font: 12px/18px 돋움, Dotum, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 112,119 등 특수번호는 해당기관 외 사용불가</div><div style="font: 12px/18px 돋움, Dotum, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;">&nbsp;</div><div style="font: 12px/18px 돋움, Dotum, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;">&nbsp; &nbsp;-. 사전등록 전 예약문자</div><div style="font: 12px/18px 돋움, Dotum, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><b>10월 11일 이전</b><span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>: 등록하지 않은 회신번호 &nbsp;전송가능</div><div style="font: 12px/18px 돋움, Dotum, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><b>10월 12일 이후</b><span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>: 등록하지 않은 회신번호 전송불가</div><div style="font: 12px/18px 돋움, Dotum, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;">* 사용할 모든 회신번호는 인증 후 등록 처리하여야 합니다. (기존 사용번호도 동일) &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</div><div style="font: 12px/18px 돋움, Dotum, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"></div><div style="font: 12px/18px 돋움, Dotum, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;"><span style="line-height: 1.5; font-family: 맑은고딕;" font-size:="" 10pt;"="">■&nbsp;</span><b>회신번호 등록 방법</b>&nbsp;</div><div style="font: 12px/18px 돋움, Dotum, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;">&nbsp; &nbsp;-.<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><span style="color: rgb(8, 121, 180);"><b>회원정보 수정 --&gt; 본인 및 담당자 인증 --&gt;회신번호 관리에서 등록</b></span></div><div style="font: 12px/18px 돋움, Dotum, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretc